671
00:35:14,880 --> 00:35:15,440
Shu Han.

672
00:35:16,039 --> 00:35:17,440
Shu Han went with him.

673
00:35:19,440 --> 00:35:20,039
Cousin,

674
00:35:21,119 --> 00:35:22,239
aren't you curious

675
00:35:22,239 --> 00:35:23,199
