709
00:36:27,800 --> 00:36:29,840
Yeah!

710
00:36:30,000 --> 00:36:30,800
Yeah!

711
00:36:31,119 --> 00:36:32,599
Yeah!

712
00:37:42,719 --> 00:37:44,639
Kiss, kiss, kiss!

713
00:37:44,639 --> 00:37:45,519
Kiss, kiss, kiss!

714
00:37:45,599 --> 00:37:49,280
Kiss, kiss, kiss!

715
00:37:50,280 --> 00:37:51,199
Where did you kiss?

716
00:37:51,760 --> 00:37:52,679
On the lips!

717
00:37:52,679 --> 00:37:53,719
On the lips!

718
