751
00:39:36,880 --> 00:39:37,559
Thanks.

752
00:39:38,000 --> 00:39:38,800
Thank you.

753
00:39:39,719 --> 00:39:40,679
Congratulations.

754
00:39:41,239 --> 00:39:41,880
Congratulations.
Thank you.

755
00:39:43,639 --> 00:39:45,000
