796
00:41:19,960 --> 00:41:20,800
Take care on the road.

797
00:41:22,239 --> 00:41:22,960
I'm off then.

798
00:41:23,519 --> 00:41:23,840
So,
you're not waiting?

799
00:41:26,239 --> 00:41:26,840
Alright, go ahead.
Go ahead.

800
00:41:27,519 --> 00:41:28,199
